{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":800,"text":"In India, we have these huge families."},{"time":3840,"text":"I bet a lot of you all\nmust have heard about it."},{"time":6440,"text":"Which means that there are\na lot of family events."},{"time":9840,"text":"So as a child, my parents\nused to drag me to these family events."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14360,"text":"But the one thing\nthat I always looked forward to"},{"time":17400,"text":"was playing around with my cousins."},{"time":20160,"text":"And there was always this one uncle"},{"time":22480,"text":"who used to be there,"},{"time":23760,"text":"always ready, jumping around with us,"},{"time":25640,"text":"having games for us,"},{"time":27160,"text":"making us kids have the time of our lives."},{"time":30920,"text":"This man was extremely successful:"},{"time":33280,"text":"he was confident and powerful."},{"time":35920,"text":"But then I saw this hale and hearty person\ndeteriorate in health."},{"time":41240,"text":"He was diagnosed with Parkinson's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44760,"text":"Parkinson's is a disease that causes\ndegeneration of the nervous system,"},{"time":48840,"text":"which means that this person\nwho used to be independent"},{"time":51840,"text":"suddenly finds tasks like drinking coffee,\nbecause of tremors, much more difficult."},{"time":57800,"text":"My uncle started using a walker to walk,"},{"time":60480,"text":"and to take a turn,"},{"time":61720,"text":"he literally had to take\none step at a time, like this,"},{"time":65800,"text":"and it took forever."},{"time":68240,"text":"So this person, who used to be\nthe center of attention"},{"time":71440,"text":"in every family gathering,"},{"time":73520,"text":"was suddenly hiding behind people."},{"time":76400,"text":"He was hiding from the pitiful look\nin people's eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80440,"text":"And he's not the only one in the world."},{"time":83280,"text":"Every year, 60,000 people\nare newly diagnosed with Parkinson's,"},{"time":88800,"text":"and this number is only rising."},{"time":92360,"text":"As designers, we dream that our designs\nsolve these multifaceted problems,"},{"time":97800,"text":"one solution that solves it all,"},{"time":100640,"text":"but it need not always be like that."},{"time":103680,"text":"You can also target simple problems"},{"time":106520,"text":"and create small solutions for them\nand eventually make a big impact."},{"time":111120,"text":"So my aim here was\nto not cure Parkinson's,"},{"time":114520,"text":"but to make their everyday tasks\nmuch more simple,"},{"time":117720,"text":"and then make an impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120040,"text":"Well, the first thing I targeted\nwas tremors, right?"},{"time":124440,"text":"My uncle told me that he had stopped\ndrinking coffee or tea in public"},{"time":129000,"text":"just out of embarrassment,"},{"time":131000,"text":"so, well, I designed the no-spill cup."},{"time":135080,"text":"It works just purely on its form."},{"time":137960,"text":"The curve on top deflects the liquid\nback inside every time they have tremors,"},{"time":143240,"text":"and this keeps the liquid inside\ncompared to a normal cup."},{"time":146800,"text":"But the key here is that it is not tagged\nas a Parkinson's patient product."},{"time":152040,"text":"It looks like a cup that could be used\nby you, me, any clumsy person,"},{"time":156480,"text":"and that makes it much more comforting\nfor them to use, to blend in."},{"time":161920,"text":"So, well, one problem solved,"},{"time":164600,"text":"many more to go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166640,"text":"All this while, I was interviewing him,"},{"time":169080,"text":"questioning him,"},{"time":170640,"text":"and then I realized that I was getting\nvery superficial information,"},{"time":174360,"text":"or just answers to my questions."},{"time":177200,"text":"But I really needed to dig deeper\nto get a new perspective."},{"time":181000,"text":"So I thought, well,\nlet's observe him in his daily tasks,"},{"time":184760,"text":"while he's eating, while he's watching TV."},{"time":187800,"text":"And then, when I was actually\nobserving him walking to his dining table,"},{"time":191880,"text":"it struck me, this man who finds it\nso difficult to walk on flat land,"},{"time":197080,"text":"how does he climb a staircase?"},{"time":199320,"text":"Because in India we do not have\na fancy rail that takes you up a staircase"},{"time":203040,"text":"like in the developed countries."},{"time":205080,"text":"One actually has to climb the stairs."},{"time":207920,"text":"So he told me,"},{"time":209200,"text":"\"Well, let me show you how I do it.\""},{"time":211880,"text":"Let's take a look at what I saw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216960,"text":"So he took really long\nto reach this position,"},{"time":219640,"text":"and then all this while, I'm thinking,"},{"time":221520,"text":"\"Oh my God, is he really going to do it?"},{"time":223480,"text":"Is he really, really going to do it\nwithout his walker?\""},{"time":226400,"text":"And then ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":236680,"text":"And the turns, he took them so easily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241240,"text":"So -- shocked?"},{"time":242920,"text":"Well, I was too."},{"time":247320,"text":"So this person who could not\nwalk on flat land"},{"time":250320,"text":"was suddenly a pro at climbing stairs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253720,"text":"On researching this, I realized that\nit's because it's a continuous motion."},{"time":258399,"text":"There's this other man\nwho also suffers from the same symptoms"},{"time":261560,"text":"and uses a walker,"},{"time":263000,"text":"but the moment he's put on a cycle,"},{"time":265120,"text":"all his symptoms vanish,"},{"time":266840,"text":"because it is a continuous motion."},{"time":269560,"text":"So the key for me was to translate\nthis feeling of walking on a staircase"},{"time":273880,"text":"back to flat land."},{"time":275880,"text":"And a lot of ideas\nwere tested and tried on him,"},{"time":278840,"text":"but the one that finally worked\nwas this one. Let's take a look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":288520,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293000,"text":"He walked faster, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":294480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":299240,"text":"I call this the staircase illusion,"},{"time":302040,"text":"and actually when the staircase illusion\nabruptly ended, he froze,"},{"time":306640,"text":"and this is called freezing of gait."},{"time":308680,"text":"So it happens a lot,"},{"time":309920,"text":"so why not have a staircase illusion\nflowing through all their rooms,"},{"time":313880,"text":"making them feel much more confident?"},{"time":317440,"text":"You know, technology is not always it."},{"time":320120,"text":"What we need are human-centered solutions."},{"time":322920,"text":"I could have easily\nmade it into a projection,"},{"time":325160,"text":"or a Google Glass, or something like that."},{"time":327520,"text":"But I stuck to simple print on the floor."},{"time":330360,"text":"This print could be taken into hospitals"},{"time":333320,"text":"to make them feel much more welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336600,"text":"What I wish to do\nis make every Parkinson's patient"},{"time":339720,"text":"feel like my uncle felt that day."},{"time":342200,"text":"He told me that I made him feel\nlike his old self again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347120,"text":"\"Smart\" in today's world\nhas become synonymous to high tech,"},{"time":351960,"text":"and the world is only getting\nsmarter and smarter day by day."},{"time":355800,"text":"But why can't smart be something\nthat's simple and yet effective?"},{"time":360320,"text":"All we need is a little bit of empathy\nand some curiosity,"},{"time":364320,"text":"to go out there, observe."},{"time":366600,"text":"But let's not stop at that."},{"time":368520,"text":"Let's find these complex problems.\nDon't be scared of them."},{"time":372200,"text":"Break them, boil them down\ninto much smaller problems,"},{"time":375800,"text":"and then find simple solutions for them."},{"time":378320,"text":"Test these solutions, fail if needed,"},{"time":381360,"text":"but with newer insights to make it better."},{"time":384240,"text":"Imagine what we all could do\nif we all came up with simple solutions."},{"time":388520,"text":"What would the world be like\nif we combined all our simple solutions?"},{"time":392880,"text":"Let's make a smarter world,\nbut with simplicity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397160,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}